text:
This dashboard showcases developed workflows within the B-cubed project for the region of Flanders, a region of Europe where species occurrence data are abundant.
The implemented indicators in this dashboard can be subdivided into:

General biodiversity indicators (based on b3gbi, for instance, cumulative species richness, relative species richness, etc.);
Phylogenetic indicators (based on pdindicatoR);
Invasive Alien Species indicators (based on impIndicator, TRIAS and b3alien)
